      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Ibn Mahboub, from Al A’ala, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The tranquillity (Mentioned in 48:4) is the faith’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Khalid from ibn Mahbub from al-‘Ala’ from Muhammad ibn Muslim from abu Ja’far (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu Ja’far (a.s.) has said, ‘Serenity (al-Sakinah) is belief.” "
        ]
      }
